---
title: Ground Chicken Fajita Bowls with Spanish-Style Rice
description: This dinner brings all the customizable flavours of chicken fajitas to your table in bowl form! Using delicious Spanish-style tomato rice as the base, dress your own bowl and enjoy dinner as you like it!
